OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783892996
OL,3,CTrump ally Senator Lindsey Graham dies
OL,4,Cafter 'sudden illness'
OL,6,FUS senator Lindsey Graham, one of
OL,7,FPresident Donald Trump's closest
OL,8,Fallies in Congress, has died "after a
OL,9,Fbrief and sudden illness", his office
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FHis office did not provide any
OL,13,Fadditional details about the South
OL,14,FCarolina Republican and said his
OL,15,Ffamily "appreciates prayers at this
OL,16,Ftime and asks for privacy during this
OL,17,Fincredibly difficult period."
OL,26,@wD@HOUyD@]O]
