OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783892996
OL,3,CTrump ally Senator Lindsey Graham dies
OL,4,Cafter 'sudden illness'
OL,6,FThe senator had just returned from
OL,7,FKyiv, where he met Ukrainian President
OL,8,FVolodymyr Zelenskyy on Friday, the day
OL,9,Fbefore he died.
OL,11,FFirst elected to the US Senate in 2002
OL,12,Fafter serving in the House, Graham
OL,13,Fbriefly ran for president in 2016 and
OL,14,Fclashed with Trump, criticizing him as
OL,15,F"unfit for office."
OL,17,FHowever, he later emerged as one of
OL,18,FTrump's top allies, speaking with him
OL,19,Ffrequently and becoming a regular
OL,20,Fpresence on the golf course alongside
OL,21,Fthe president.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@SO]
