CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783892996
OL,3,CTrump ally Senator Lindsey Graham dies
OL,4,Cafter 'sudden illness'
OL,6,FGraham advised the president on
OL,7,Fforeign policy matters such as Iran
OL,8,Fand Russia, and had just announced an
OL,9,Fagreement on Friday with the Trump
OL,10,Fadministration to move forward on a
OL,11,Fpackage of Russia sanctions.
OL,13,FHe also cheered on Trump's decision to
OL,14,Fstrike nuclear sites last year and had
OL,15,Fbeen a supporter of the latest
OL,16,Fconflict that started a few months ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
