OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783892996
OL,3,CTrump ally Senator Lindsey Graham dies
OL,4,Cafter 'sudden illness'
OL,6,F"Senator Lindsey Graham, one of the
OL,7,Fgreatest people and Senators I have
OL,8,Fever known, is dead!" Trump posted on
OL,9,Fsocial media early Sunday morning. "He
OL,10,Fwas always working, and was a true
OL,11,FAmerican Patriot. Lindsey will be
OL,12,Fgreatly missed!!! DETAILS AND
OL,13,FARRANGEMENTS TO FOLLOW. So sad!"
